       <HR>
       <FONT size="+1"> Analgesic tablet of <B><I>aspirin</I></B> and caffeine containing low-substituted
     hydroxypropyl cellulose
</FONT><BR>
       <BR><CENTER><b>Abstract</b></CENTER>
       <p>An analogesic tablet containing <B><I>aspirin,</I></B> acetaminophen and caffeine of
     improved dissolution rate containing low-substituted
     hydroxypropylcellulose.
</p>
