15  minutes in a Twin Shell Blender.  D. Add stearic acid to (C) and mix for five  minutes.  E. Compress to specifications shown below.  Appearance: White Tablets  Punch: 7/16"  Tablet Weight: 674.0 mg.  Thickness: 0.245" .+-. 0.005"  Hardness: 15-20 SCU
