<BR><BR>As is clear from Table V, tablets CY 3513-1 are acceptable only when packaged in a slide box.  Tablets CW 3446-58, however, were acceptable under all the storage conditions; that is to say, they had an acceptable dissolution rate.  As to
stability, these respective products are quite comparable.
